  <prompt>Replace the current App.tsx layout with the new narrative design. Remove: AiBriefing import/usage, NarrativeSummary import/usage, ChannelCard accordion pattern, PreferencesPanel at bottom. Add: TldrSection (top), ActivityNotesSection (middle), CaughtUpFooter (bottom). Update DigestHeader: remove Mark All Read button, add PreferencesDropdown gear icon (right side). Wire useBriefingNarration hook replacing useAiBriefing. Pass channelNarratives to ActivityNotesSection. Wire useInlineTodoCreate for To Do actions. Wire dismiss handler (mark appnotification as read). After wiring is complete, delete old component files: AiBriefing.tsx, NarrativeSummary.tsx, ChannelCard.tsx, NotificationItem.tsx, PreferencesPanel.tsx.</prompt>
  <role>SPAARKE platform developer.</role>
  <goal>App.tsx renders the narrative memo layout, old dashboard components removed</goal>
  <context>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/solutions/DailyBriefing/src/App.tsx</file>
